## Installation:

mkdir ~/.config/leftwm/themes/marooned
cp -R ./marooned ~/.config/leftwm/themes/marooned
ln -s ~/.config/leftwm/themes/marooned ~/.config/leftwm/themes/current
mv ~/.Xresources ~/.Xresources.old
pkill leftwm-worker
